Package: exdex
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of the Extremal Index
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2019-07-27
Authors@R: c(
    person(c("Paul", "J."), "Northrop", email = "p.northrop@ucl.ac.uk", 
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Constantinos", "Christodoulides", role = c("aut", "cph"))
    )
Description: Performs frequentist inference for the extremal index of a 
  stationary time series using the methodologies described in 
  Northrop (2015) <doi:10.1007/s10687-015-0221-5>,
  Berghaus and Bucher (2018) <doi:10.1214/17-AOS1621>
  Suveges (2007) <doi:10.1007/s10687-007-0034-2>
  and
  Suveges and Davison (2010)  <doi:10.1214/09-AOAS292>.
